      • hasCamera

        public static boolean hasCamera(Context context)
        Checks camera availability based on API level.
        Change "android.hardware.camera.front" and "android.hardware.camera.any" to PackageManager#FEATURE_CAMERA_FRONT and PackageManager#FEATURE_CAMERA_ANY, respectively, once they become accessible or minSdk version is incremented.
        Parameters:
        context - -Context.
        Returns:
        boolean - true If the device has camera, else false.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if any of the parameters is null.
        See Also:
        PackageManager#hasSystemFeature(String)}.
